ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - British Columbia Avian Influenza Assistance
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an AGREEMENT with BRITISH COLUMBIA and provide contributions of up to $1,350,000 in order to help poultry producers in the province manage the extraordinary recovery costs resulting from the AVIAN INFLUENZA OUTBREAK.
